  "meta": {
    "name": "Reconcile untracked vault MON (recurring, post-V2-migration)",
    "description": "Sweeps VaultBuybackBurnV2 and VaultLPSupport for MON received via the FeeRouter's raw-send path (untracked in the per-token pendingBurn/pendingLP mappings since the last reconcile), then re-deposits each amount via VaultRecouper.recover() attributed to the correct token, per-token (not lumped into a single token). Balances/amounts computed fresh at generation time from live on-chain FeeRouted events. Re-verify balances immediately before executing if significant time has passed, since fees accrue continuously.",
    "txBuilderVersion": "1.16.5"
  },
